{
  "version": "2026-03-12",
  "notes": [
    "Partition is recovered from the raw queue field at analysis time.",
    "Conte and Stampede queue and host identifiers are anonymized in FRESCO, so those clusters use cluster-wide hardware defaults.",
    "node_memory_gb values are expressed in GB-scale units to match peak_memory_gb derived from value_memused_max.",
    "gpu_count_per_node counts NVIDIA-style GPUs only; Intel Xeon Phi coprocessors are represented via node_type."
